<br>
At the beginning, the post said the armor was nerfed.  I have the below tunic and was just wondering what the stats were before the nerf as 24 AC is very nice for a Druid BP and is only 2 less AC then the CC BP that drops in Velks (which is much harder to get).<br>
<br>
Elysian Tunic<br>
MAGIC ITEM  NO DROP<br>
Slot: CHEST<br>
AC: 24   WT: 7.0<br>
STR+15  STA+5  WIS+15  HP+15  MANA+75  SV<br>
POISON+8  SV DISEASE+8  SV COLD+8  SV FIRE+8  SV MAGIC+8  <br>
<br>
Armor looks like silver chain on Elfs.  It looks like a dull silver chain on Humans and Halflings.  The helm has a graphic on Humans and Halflings.  I too will be using Elysian as my armor of choice for the rest of my life in Norrath (unless the next expansions come out with something much better).  Druing my 6 days in UP I have seen about 6 boots, 5 leggs, 8 bracers, 1 helm, 2 tunics, 3 arms, 2 or 3 gloves and about 10 spells includign SoE.  I currently am currently wearing all Elysian other then the wrists and hands.  You can see what it looks like on a human druid by clicking the below link.<br>
